    </ul>
    <p>By purchasing and using our products, you acknowledge and accept these limitations.</p>

    <h2>7. No Liability for Misuse</h2>
    <p>GetPawsy assumes no responsibility for:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Use of products in ways not intended or recommended</li>
      <li>Failure to follow product care and safety instructions</li>
      <li>Failure to properly supervise pets during product use</li>
      <li>Use of products by pets for which they are not sized or intended</li>
      <li>Continued use of damaged or worn products</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>8. Product-Specific Safety Notes</h2>
    <h3>Toys</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Replace toys when they show signs of wear</li>
      <li>Remove squeakers if they become exposed</li>
      <li>Do not leave rope toys with unsupervised pets</li>
    </ul>
    <h3>Beds & Bedding</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Check for exposed stuffing regularly</li>
      <li>Ensure zippers and fasteners are secure</li>
      <li>Keep away from heat sources</li>
    </ul>
    <h3>Collars, Harnesses & Leashes</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Ensure proper fit (2 fingers should fit under collar)</li>
      <li>Check hardware for rust or damage</li>
      <li>Never leave a leashed pet unattended</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>9. Reporting Safety Issues</h2>
    <p>If you experience a safety issue with any GetPawsy product, please contact us immediately:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Email:</strong> safety@getpawsy.com</li>
      <li><strong>Subject:</strong> Product Safety Report</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Your reports help us improve product safety for all pets.</p>

    <h2>10. Recall Information</h2>
    <p>In the event of a product recall, we will:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Notify affected customers via email</li>
      <li>Post recall information on our website</li>
      <li>Provide instructions for returns or refunds</li>
      <li>Report to appropriate regulatory authorities</li>
    </ul>

